title: AMAZING: Watch These Men Walk On A Frozen Crystal Clear Lake
text:
Posted on
AMAZING: Watch These Men Walk On A Frozen Crystal Clear Lake.
These two men captured some amazing footage as they walked across what looks like glass.
They were spending their day on a frozen mountain lake in High Tatras Mountains in Slovakia.
The scenery is absolutely breath taking!
